data.value: Here is a list of every variant a Material Button can be. Contained button's shadows are only drawn at run-time. Click on them and checkout those sweet animations. Oh yeah, the buttons follow the theme and colors, try changing those too. Normally the buttons should be AutoSize = true, but for the sake of my OCD, it's set to false here If any of the buttons looks weird while designing, change the tab background color from transparent to white.
